CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page A20, reads: "The Restland Lincoln Memorial Park booth was well represented by Euthlaw Blair, Agnes Williams, N.R. Conn, Ronald D. McDaniel, William F. Hayward, Thomas Logan, Connie Nash, James C. Rago, and Darwin Taylor."
TitMainTitle: Three men, and woman wearing fur and hat standing in Restland-Lincoln Memorial Park booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
